## 🚀 Optimized Version (Recommended)

Your current solution works, but we can optimize space.

```cpp id="p8xq2a"
class Solution {
public:
    int largestAltitude(vector<int>& gain) {
        int current = 0;
        int maxAlt = 0;

        for (int x : gain) {
            current += x;
            maxAlt = max(maxAlt, current);
        }

        return maxAlt;
    }
};
```

